{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "03", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "18", "M": "58", "S": "27"}}, "news": [{"title": "Over 1.28 lakh pending land survey cases in Maharashtra", "para": "Maharashtra faces a backlog of over 1.28 lakh land survey cases, with resolutions averaging 121 days. The state is set to appoint licensed surveyors by March 2026, establishing clear criteria for their selection and operation. Plans are also in motion to adopt a system similar to other states, where property is officially measured before land sale deeds are registered, ensuring accurate records and streamlining the process.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/maharashtra-faces-over-128-lakh-pending-land-survey-cases/132163718?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-30102/132163718.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Haryana RERA directs BPTP to refund maintenance charges to allottee with 11% interest", "para": "Haryana RERA\u2019s Gurugram bench has directed BPTP to refund \u20b91.16 lakh collected as maintenance charges before handing over possession of a unit in Park Spacio, Sector 37D, Gurugram. The authority also awarded \u20b91 lakh as compensation and \u20b950,000 as litigation cost.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/rera/haryana-rera-orders-bptp-to-refund-116-lakh-in-unlawful-maintenance-charges/132163468?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-311823/132163468.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "rera"}, {"title": "Protected Aravali land cleared of illegal walls, buildings in Gurugram", "para": "Authorities in Gurugram have reclaimed nearly three acres of protected Aravali land in Behrampur village, demolishing 11 illegal structures. This significant anti-encroachment drive targeted under-construction buildings and boundary walls on land vital for groundwater recharge and wildlife corridors. The action follows years of efforts to protect this ecologically sensitive region from unauthorized development and fragmentation.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/massive-anti-encroachment-drive-clears-protected-aravali-land-in-gurugram/132163699?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-2671348/132163699.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}